OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome light and patchy rain during the
OL,7,Fevening. Clear spells perhaps
OL,8,Fdeveloping, before further cloud and
OL,9,Frain arrives from the west towards
OL,10,Fdawn, this persistent and occasionally
OL,11,Fheavy. Becoming windy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FWind and rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes, clearing away eastwards by
OL,15,Fearly afternoon. Sunny spells then
OL,16,Fdeveloping, also blustery heavy
OL,17,Fshowers with a risk of thunder and
OL,18,Fsnow on high ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
