OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunshine
OL,6,Fand showers Sunday and Monday, these
OL,7,Fpotentially heavy and thundery.
OL,8,FPerhaps drier and brighter Tuesday.
OL,9,FWindy on Sunday, then easing.
OL,10,FTemperatures mostly around average,
OL,11,Fbut overnight frost is possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
